{
  "hooks": {
    "SessionStart": [
      {
        "matcher": "*",
        "hooks": [{
          "type": "command",
          "command": "\"C:/Program Files/Git/bin/bash.exe\" \"C:/Users/whflo/.claude/plugins/cache/claude-plugins-official/undercurrent/55b58ec6e564/hooks/session-start\"",
          "async": false
        }]
      }
    ],
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Bash",
        "hooks": [{
          "type": "command",
          "command": "\"C:/Program Files/Git/bin/bash.exe\" \"C:/Users/whflo/.claude/plugins/cache/claude-plugins-official/undercurrent/55b58ec6e564/hooks/scripts/post-bash-dispatch.sh\"",
          "async": false
        }]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Write|Edit",
        "hooks": [{
          "type": "command",
          "command": "\"C:/Program Files/Git/bin/bash.exe\" \"C:/Users/whflo/.claude/plugins/cache/claude-plugins-official/undercurrent/55b58ec6e564/hooks/scripts/post-edit-dispatch.sh\"",
          "async": false
        }]
      }
    ],
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Write|Edit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "\"C:/Program Files/Git/bin/bash.exe\" \"C:/Users/whflo/.claude/plugins/cache/claude-plugins-official/undercurrent/55b58ec6e564/hooks/scripts/migration-linter.sh\"",
            "async": false
          },
          {
            "type": "prompt",
            "prompt": "Check the tool input. If the file_path contains 'src/app/(dashboard)/', inject this reminder: 'Dashboard route detected. Verify: (1) middleware.ts matcher includes this path, (2) API routes have path.startsWith() auth, (3) server components use getUser(). See security-posture skill.'"
          },
          {
            "type": "prompt",
            "prompt": "Check the tool input. If the code being written contains Supabase/PostgREST calls (.from(, .select(, .update(, .upsert(, .insert(, .delete(, .rpc(), supabase.), apply these 8 gotchas: (1) No .update().or().select() — read-then-write. (2) .in() chunk under 50K rows. (3) Upsert needs ALL NOT NULL columns. (4) max_rows 50K hard cap. (5) No .maybeSingle() after .update(). (6) Bad .select() column = silent null. (7) ntile() on deduplicated set. (8) Never re-query fetched data. See database-query-safety skill."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Write",
        "hooks": [{
          "type": "command",
          "command": "\"C:/Program Files/Git/bin/bash.exe\" \"C:/Users/whflo/.claude/plugins/cache/claude-plugins-official/undercurrent/55b58ec6e564/hooks/scripts/plan-file-guard.sh\"",
          "async": false
        }]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Bash",
        "hooks": [{
          "type": "prompt",
          "prompt": "Check the tool input. If the command contains 'git push': (1) Check for untracked files imported by committed code. (2) Verify tests pass. (3) Confirm documentation.md updated if architectural files changed. (4) Never force-push to master. Warn before proceeding if any check would fail."
        }]
      }
    ],
    "PreCompact": [
      {
        "matcher": "*",
        "hooks": [{
          "type": "command",
          "command": "\"C:/Program Files/Git/bin/bash.exe\" \"C:/Users/whflo/.claude/plugins/cache/claude-plugins-official/undercurrent/55b58ec6e564/hooks/scripts/pre-compact.sh\"",
